@CoreSRE_HostAddress = http://localhost:5156

GET {{CoreSRE_HostAddress}}/weatherforecast/
Accept: application/json

###

### Resolve AgentCard from remote A2A endpoint
POST {{CoreSRE_HostAddress}}/api/agents/resolve-card
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "http://localhost:5100"
}

###

### GET /api/tools/available-functions — 查询所有可绑定工具函数
GET {{CoreSRE_HostAddress}}/api/tools/available-functions
Accept: application/json

###

### GET /api/tools/available-functions?search=&status= — 带过滤参数
GET {{CoreSRE_HostAddress}}/api/tools/available-functions?search=health&status=Active
Accept: application/json

###

### POST /api/chat/stream — 与工具绑定的 ChatClient Agent 对话（替换 agentId 为实际值）
POST {{CoreSRE_HostAddress}}/api/chat/stream
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "threadId": "{{$guid}}",
  "runId": "{{$guid}}",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "请检查一下系统的健康状态"
    }
  ],
  "context": [
    { "description": "agentId", "value": "YOUR-CHATCLIENT-AGENT-ID-HERE" }
  ]
}

###
